         TITLE 'FILEA - MAPSET FOR LOW BALANCE REPORT - COBOL'
***********************************************************************
*                                                                     *
* MODULE NAME = DFH0CMD                                               *
*                                                                     *
* DESCRIPTIVE NAME = Report Map for Sample Application                *
*                                                                     *
*                                                                     *
